uantum Monte Carlo simulations confirm this\nmetal-organic crystal to be a very good spin-1/2 Heisenberg antiferromagnet\nwith a low saturation field H s of 1.75 T.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Dec 2021 16:03:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 05:36:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-22"}
