 z-position\nresolution for gamma interactions in the 0.3 MeVee to 0.4 MeVee range to be\n2.24 cm$\\pm$1.10 cm and 1.45 cm$\\pm$0.19 cm for silicone optical coupling pad\nand optical grease, respectively. The observed interaction time resolution is\n265 ps$\\pm$29 ps and 235 ps$\\pm$10 ps for silicone optical coupling pad and\noptical grease, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Dec 2021 17:41:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
