laden viscoelastic flow\nconfigurations with $O(10^5-10^6)$ rigid spheres that are representative of\nhydraulic fracture operations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Dec 2021 20:01:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-22"}
