on par with\nother proposed models in the literature, including flexible deep learning ones.\nFinally, selected theoretical results and empirical performance of the proposed\nmethodology on synthetic data are reported which justify the good performance\nof the proposed method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 05:00:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-04"}
