nting problem motivated by a paper by B. Spivak and A.\nZyuzin of 2004 about wave scattering in a disordered nonlinear medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 14:22:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Feb 2022 11:11:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 08:58:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-11"}
