converges, when\n$\\alpha_A/d\\to\\infty$, to the weight distribution $P(w)$ for infinitely narrow\ndistributions (i.e., $\\tau \\to \\infty, \\,\\forall w_c$) as well as for $w_c\\to0,\n\\, \\forall\\tau$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 15:22:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 May 2022 13:19:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
