ential security problems related to base-images\nand encourage them to investigate base-images from security perspective before\ndeveloping their applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 07:41:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-24"}
